  "texts": [
    "This suggests that the presence of domain-specific expert models positively impacts the overall performance of the MoFE model, indicating that knowledge transfer from the expert models-specifically the FFN blocks-occurs within the MoFE architecture.",
    "Building on the previous experiment confirming knowledge transfer in the medical domain, we investigate whether knowledge transfer across multiple domains is possible and how the number of domain-specific expert models affects the MoFE model's domain knowledge.",
    "For this, we develop a finance expert model by training TinyLlama on the Sujet-Finance-Instruct-177k dataset foot_0, split Table 5: Task performance of the MoFE models with different base models.",
    "9:1 for training and testing.",
    "We then construct medium-sized MoFE models with varying numbers of medical expert models and finance expert models and evaluate them on MedMCQA and the Sujet-Finance-Instruct-177k test set."
  ]
}